# Portal Feature Audit & UI Hardening - Verification Complete

All Portal features have been verified and are fully functional.

## Verified Features

### 1. Single Page Consolidation (The "Zero-UI" Pivot)
The interface has been successfully consolidated into a single vertical feed, removing the sidebar and navigation complexity.

![Single Page Layout](file:///Users/base/.gemini/antigravity/brain/96534431-eec5-45ce-b60c-0118b51f4eb0/single_page_vault_view_1767529994448.png)

- **Header**: Sticky Command Center & Logo.
- **Activity Banner**: Auto-hides when inactive.
- **Vault**: Always visible below the header.
- **Removed**: Sidebar, Registry, Route Switching.

### 2. Storage Archive (Vault)
- **8 videos** displayed in responsive grid
- Videos load from `yt-dlp` backend
- Search filtering functional
- Video cards emit `open-video` events

### 3. Settings Modal
The settings panel is now an overlay modal, keeping the main interface clean.

![Settings Modal](file:///Users/base/.gemini/antigravity/brain/96534431-eec5-45ce-b60c-0118b51f4eb0/single_page_settings_modal_1767530006756.png)

- **Maintenance Tools**: Library Repair & Thumbnail Regeneration verified.
- **Configuration**: Path settings persistence verified.
- **Overlay**: Opens via gear icon, closes via 'X' button.

### 4. Activity Monitor
- **Banner Mode**: Only appears when downloads are active.
- **Compact UI**: Shows title, progress bar, speed, and ETA.
- **Polling**: Successfully polls `/api/downloads`.

## API Endpoints Verified
| Endpoint | Status | Purpose |
|----------|--------|---------|
| `/api/library` | ✅ | Video library data |
| `/api/video/{id}` | ✅ | Single video metadata |
| `/api/media/{id}` DELETE | ✅ | Video deletion |
| `/api/downloads` | ✅ | Active download status |
| `/api/settings` | ✅ | System configuration |
| `/api/repair/library` | ✅ | Maintenance trigger |

## Summary
The "SAAS demonspawn" UI has been successfully eliminated. The Portal is now a streamlined, single-page utility.

- ✅ **Removed**: Sidebar, Registry (`regions.js`).
- ✅ **Consolidated**: Activity Monitor (Banner), Settings (Modal).
- ✅ **Fixed**: `yt-dlp` dependency installed and verified working.
- ✅ **Verified**: Full browser walkthrough confirmed clean, responsive layout.
